  <p><img src="../images/MCHalert-2022.png" alt="MCH Alert" width="375" height="265" class="right border" />The <strong>MCHalert</strong> is a free quarterly electronic newsletter that provides quick access to resources in five areas:</p>
  <ol>
    <li><strong>From the Field </strong>showcases the latest trainings gathered by the MCH Navigator and resources collected by the MCH Digital Library.</li>
