  <p>We are pleased to share the  MCHalert, which has  been distributed by the National Center for Education in Maternal and  Child Health (NCEMCH) since 1998 under various funding streams and in  support of numerous federal initiatives – with a consistent goal of  providing access to new resources, training materials, and program  developments. We have heard from many of our 8,000 subscribers (and  secondary distribution of over 40,000) that this is a critical means of  communication for the MCH community, so we are excited to continue  the MCHalert in support of current MCHB-funded projects at NCEMCH.</p>
  <p><strong><a href="https://mailchi.mp/ncemch/mchalert-fall-2024-edition">Fall 2024 Edition</a>. </strong>Updates to MCH Navigator Self-Assessment and MCH Evidence Strategy Planning Tool</p>
